  <!-- Posibles errores -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students do not use the length of the given unit fraction to locate 1.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>During the launch of the next day's activity, have students complete a choral count by thirds, starting at <m>\frac{1}{3}</m>. Have students raise their hand, stop the count, and explain their reasoning when they get to the fraction that is equivalent to 1.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>